msgid "Framework Django per pannelli admin: template tag riusabili, design system SCSS, JavaScript vanilla a moduli ES. Questa pagina mostra i componenti documentati nello styleguide con snippet copia-incollabili."
msgstr "A Django framework for admin panels: reusable template tags, SCSS design system, vanilla ES modules JavaScript. This page shows the documented components in the styleguide with copy-paste snippets."

msgid "Lingua"
msgstr "Language"

msgid "Naviga le sezioni dalla sidebar a sinistra. Aggiungere"
msgstr "Browse sections from the left sidebar. Append"

msgid "alla URL nasconde la sidebar (utile per modali / iframe)."
msgstr "to the URL to hide the sidebar (useful for modals / iframes)."

msgid "Grafici da tabella (Chart.js)"
msgstr "Charts from HTML table (Chart.js)"

msgid "Il tag <code>velora_chart_from_table</code> legge una tabella HTML e disegna un grafico <code>line</code>, <code>bar</code> o <code>pie</code> sul canvas (bundle Chart.js incluso in <code>velora.js</code>)."
msgstr "The <code>velora_chart_from_table</code> tag reads an HTML table and draws a <code>line</code>, <code>bar</code>, or <code>pie</code> chart on the canvas (Chart.js bundle included in <code>velora.js</code>)."

